text: William F. Dowd (November 11, 1943 – April 21, 2018) was an American politician who served in the New Jersey General Assembly from 1978 to 1982. He died on April 21, 2018, in Long Branch, New Jersey at age 74. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Members of the New Jersey General Assembly Category:New Jersey Republicans
title: William F. Dowd
